sentences: "Butterfly", born June 21) is a Japanese singer from Osaka Prefecture and is signed to Lantis.
ChouCho initially formed the band Lotus Lotus in 2007 when still in high school and performed covers of songs from anime.
Starting in June 2008, ChouCho began submitting videos of her singing on the Nico Nico Douga video sharing website.
On July 27, 2011, she made her major debut with her single "Kawaru Mirai" (カワルミライ, lit.
"Changing Future"), which is used as the opening theme to the 2011 anime Heaven's Memo Pad.
